OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FAn interim Bishop of Liverpool has
OL,8,Fbeen appointed after the last one
OL,9,Fstepped down following allegations of
OL,10,Fsexual assault and harassment.
OL,12,FRt Revd Ruth Worsley will become the
OL,13,Fnew suffragan Bishop of Wigan within
OL,14,Fthe Diocese of Liverpool and also the
OL,15,FInterim Bishop of Liverpool.
