OL,7,FWigan is part of the Liverpool Diocese
OL,8,Fand Downing Street said the invitation
OL,9,Ffor her to to become Interim Bishop of
OL,10,FLiverpool followed consultation with
OL,11,Fthe senior leadership team in
OL,12,FLiverpool.
OL,14,FNo 10 said she brings a wealth of
OL,15,Fexperience, having previously served
OL,16,Fas Acting Bishop of Bath and Wells and
OL,17,FActing Bishop of Coventry.
