OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FShe said: "The Diocese of Liverpool is
OL,8,Fa vibrant and faithful community, and
OL,9,FI look forward to working alongside
OL,10,Fthe leadership team, clergy, and
OL,11,Flaypeople as we navigate this season
OL,12,Ftogether. "
OL,14,FBishop Ruth is currently the Bishop of
OL,15,FTaunton and will continue in that role
OL,16,Ffor the time being with support to
OL,17,Fenable her to deal with urgent legal
OL,18,Fmatters in the Diocese of Liverpool.
