OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FIt is expected that from Easter
OL,8,Fonwards, she will assume her role
OL,9,Ffully as Interim Bishop of Liverpool.
OL,11,FOutgoing Bishop of Liverpool DrJohn
OL,12,FPerumbalath said in January he is
OL,13,F"retiring" from his role because he
OL,14,Fdoes not wish to be a "distraction".
OL,16,FIt came just days after a Channel 4
OL,17,FNews reported that the senior bishop
OL,18,Fhas been accused of sexual misconduct
OL,19,Fby two women, including another
OL,20,Fbishop, which he has denied.
