OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FOne woman accused Dr Perumbalath of
OL,8,Fkissing her without consent and
OL,9,Fgroping her, and a female bishop
OL,10,Faccused him of sexual harassment. Both
OL,11,Fincidents allegedly took place in
OL,12,FEssex in 2023.
OL,14,FAnnouncing the appointment of Bishop
OL,15,FRuth to the North West, Archbishop of
OL,16,FYork, Stephen Cottrell, said: "To all
OL,17,Fthose affected by the events that have
OL,18,Fled us here, I offer my heartfelt
OL,19,Fprayers.
