OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"The clergy and people of the Diocese
OL,8,Fof Liverpool have been in my prayers
OL,9,Fas well. This is a time for healing
OL,10,Fand for facing the challenges ahead
OL,11,Ftogether."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Diocese of
OL,14,FLiverpool said: "We welcome the
OL,15,Fdecision of the Archbishop of York to
OL,16,Fappoint Bishop Ruth to lead the
OL,17,FDiocese of Liverpool for this interim
OL,18,Fperiod.
