OL,7,F"Her experience and wisdom will be a
OL,8,Fgreat addition to the leadership of
OL,9,Four diocese over the next two years.
OL,11,F"We are very grateful to Bishop Ruth
OL,12,Ffor being willing to respond to this
OL,13,Fcall and the Diocese of Bath and Wells
OL,14,Ffor enabling her to take up this
OL,15,Fministry with us.
