OL,7,F"We look forward to welcoming her in
OL,8,Fdue course as she comes to lead our
OL,9,Fdiocese in this next phase. We move
OL,10,Fforward together, believing and
OL,11,Ftrusting in our God who is faithful
OL,12,Fand working his purpose out."
